Definition: used especially of what is legally or ethically right or proper or fitting
Example: a just and lasting peace- A.Lincoln; a kind and just man; a just reward; his just inheritance
Synonyms: noun, attribute, justness, UNJUST, FAIR, HONORABLE, RIGHT, RIGHTEOUS, used, especially, of, what, is, legally, or, ethically, right, proper, fitting, a, just, and, lasting, peace, -, A, Lincoln, kind, man, reward, his, inheritance
Category: adj.all
